Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小花火戴耳环了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个是耳饰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 没有打耳洞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕疼所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让人欲火中烧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 别看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的 没在看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作为赔罪跟我去宾馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 为了奖励跟我去宾馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么乱七八糟的 不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 节奏都被打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去宾馆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:40.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 宾馆宾馆的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只会说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你脑子里就只想着做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:49.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能算理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以算哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别小瞧性欲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就想和你#$*&%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太过着急的话……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}正好我也来了兴致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 明明就说过慢慢来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:12.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 等着我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 有人叫我去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我做的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:31.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服会拉长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:40.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是我想看的电影 说不定会很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 好想牵住你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你会回头看我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:00.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人也没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:13.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 明明是想看的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却完全看不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:23.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在真的就像是和麦两人独处一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在电影院里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,离得这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:30.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H95&\fn@方正中倩_GBK\t(0,600,\alpha&H00&)\bord0\fs85\frz270\pos(336,521)}我愛你！至死不渝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@方正中倩_GBK\bord0\fs85\pos(321.333,610.333)}我从未知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@方正中倩_GBK\bord0\fs85\pos(337.333,547)}恋愛成真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.49,Kuzu_text,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@方正中倩_GBK\bord0\fs85\pos(394.333,486.333)}是一件如此幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.54,Kuzu_text,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么无法实现的恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有不幸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:47.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的喜欢是「即使这样也可以」的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱就算无法实现也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不过是自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是happyend的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺有趣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么说太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我想看的电影嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是很无聊的话会感觉对不住你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算很无聊的话 那也是电影的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可不用在意那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:33.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦对刚才的事会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 麦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是牵着手一起入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像就会做同一个梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,…什么的 想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:55.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 现在简直就像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了我们去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 梦还没有醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:03.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:20.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那个时候我会叫住他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可悲地死缠烂打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后还是让他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:44.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那只是意气用事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有得到什么好感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有的仅仅是欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在的我已经
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连这二者的区别都无法理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:03.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想让人留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想让人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会付出任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会让人夺走任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不平等才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁 不管是谁都好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我觉得自己是有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:20.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时我已变得这么「女人」了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最初也只是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想像那样和喜欢的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全无法让心满足呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:43.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不用在意我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:02.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快笑 今天不是很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已经满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不保持笑脸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:07.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:15.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为发觉一切是梦的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,梦就会不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:20.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算晚上也很闷热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天陪我到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 我很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在中途就意识到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 既然怎样都实现不了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要留下快乐的回忆就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:41.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,制造出完美的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不断循环重复就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:48.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还问什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:56.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你刚才开始就完全不看我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯了不得了的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是碰到手的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被拒绝了的话 我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:10.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一生都不需要真正的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}最可 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 今天我很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:19.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这会成为我一生的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:26.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要沉睡在不会醒的梦里就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要孤身一人的话就能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:34.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…我…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就会很幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:42.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 王子大人的吻打碎了梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公主孤身一人在黑暗中醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:57.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不再哭得声嘶力竭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:03.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为不论悲伤还是喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都还未曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有想见的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要男的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,见不到小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友 我没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:25.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢 偶尔也想一个独处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:36.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦的房间 好久没来了呢 多久了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好闻的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,约会 并不开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也有与快乐同等的不满足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明知为何 却装作不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:00.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:01.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:05.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚 我早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚安呢 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 晚安妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,神大人 拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天能与麦一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,住在凡尔赛宫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要 我更喜欢姬路城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相比王子 武士更适合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快点长胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在游戏会上演王子殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没兴趣呢 演树就好了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,树真好呢 真想演一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:50.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 麦要和我在英国啊法国一起度蜜月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不行了 我们不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:57.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说组合解散了 虽然我不记得我们有拍档过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦啊啦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:06.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乖啦乖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:11.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起啦 别哭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会解散啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:14.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没你办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:27.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我知道的 我是能被允许的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:31.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一但哭泣 没有大人不感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:40.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是图书中那纯粹的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直都意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有这种自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并且加以利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要再装可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很害怕伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:56.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该是更坦率地喜欢麦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他是别人的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能做比这个更过的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:05.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道了这才是真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:08.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就和敷衍着去恋爱的人一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的喜欢他的话就应该就此打住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个呢才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不知道的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就此停下回头的话 就只会在这半吊子的感情中结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我想触碰他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再早点这样做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:42.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然 并不是说刚才的事随便怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:46.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能和喜欢的人像这样在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我意识到没有比这更想得到的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:53.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这酥麻的感觉 这热度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:57.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有现在你是只属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此甜蜜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一但知晓了就无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事也和她做过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 不喜欢吗 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是 虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在最可真的是可爱得无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使得不到你的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能因为很可爱 而继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要回应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:50.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,流星什么的 有生以来第一次看见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以稍微许了个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正卡通简体\bord0\c&H2C333B&\frz288.9\pos(888,360)}中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要是一击即中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就拿出勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:12.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就连不知道她想法这点也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要继续吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这种情况下非常卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不确认一下就不能继续的这点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 要怎么脱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:50.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个 不把丝带摘下来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 这种类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:02.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,胸…胸部不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:06.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不会比较？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会比较啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是最可的 所以想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:28.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我摸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:34.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太黑了看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样是不对的 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:44.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不污染她是为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:53.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,藕断丝连也是为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使如此我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很珍惜最可的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在麦心中我是十分特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:16.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,特别的不能侵犯的无法触摸的装饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:21.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我很希望你触摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟蹋我也好 弄脏我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:28.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想和麦活在同一个世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:33.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是无法实现的话 那种「特别」也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:45.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不需要 明明起不到任何作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:47.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不需要也无法抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,执着的证明？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:55.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是 只有这些是至今为止支撑着我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,曾是宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经 不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:30.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没意识是谁说出的想要见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:33.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但双方终于鼓足勇气说了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:40.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了 在暑假结束前好好地做出告白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:42.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:47.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而后 在暑假结束的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:51.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,决定两个人都能干脆利落地分手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:57.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后能够成为真正的恋人 手牵手地去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:03.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早点这样做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花掉太多时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:08.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 虽然根本就是以卵击石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 也是太自以为是了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:19.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对于未来的事情 虽然还什么也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
